    Class and Description
    Key
    This class provides the key for the Pitches class with reference frequencies etc.
    Pitches
    This class represents the list of pitch features for a piece of music.
  • Classes in meico.pitches used by meico.pitches 
    Class and Description
    FeatureElement
    This class represents one element of a pitch feature vector, i.e. an energy value on a frequency or chroma band and note id associations to it.
    FeatureVector
    This class represents one pitch feature, i.e. an array of FeatureElements that form the feature vector.
    Key
    This class provides the key for the Pitches class with reference frequencies etc.
